<subSubSection pageId="61" pageNumber="62" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="61.[151,1436,1014,1329]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
The 
<taxonomicName authority="Meigen, 1830" authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1830" box="[202,280,1015,1040]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scripta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[202,280,1015,1040]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">scripta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group was proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Mannheims, B." box="[646,863,1014,1041]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="113 - 136" refId="ref61679" refString="Mannheims, B. (1953) 15. Tipulidae. In: Lindner, E. (Ed.), Die Fliegen der palaearktischen Region, 3 (5) 1, Lief, 173, 113 - 136." type="journal article" year="1953">Mannheims (1953)</bibRefCitation>
, discussed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Savchenko, E. N." box="[1026,1225,1015,1041]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="143 - 216" refId="ref62891" refString="Savchenko, E. N. (1960) A contribution to the taxonomy of crane-flies (Diptera, Tipulidae) of the subgenus Vestiplex Bezzi of the genus Tipula L. Horae Societatis Entomologicae Rossicae Unionis Soveticae, 47, 143 - 216. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1960">Savchenko (1960</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Savchenko, E. N." box="[1237,1297,1015,1042]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 503" refId="ref62940" refString="Savchenko, E. N. (1964) Crane-flies (Diptera, Tipulidae), Subfam. Tipulinae, Genus Tipula L., 2. Fauna USSR, New Series, 89, Insecta Diptera, 2 (4), 1 - 503. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1964">1964</bibRefCitation>
), with range of species revised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Starkevich, P. &amp; Podenas, S." box="[389,709,1051,1077]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="141 - 147" refId="ref63233" refString="Starkevich, P. &amp; Podenas, S. (2011) A new species of long-palped crane fly in the subgenus Tipula (Vestiplex) [Diptera: Tipulidae] from the Far East of Russia. Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 137, 141 - 147. https: // doi. org / 10.3157 / 061.137.0103" type="journal article" year="2011">Starkevich &amp; Podenas (2011</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Starkevich, P. &amp; Podenas, S." box="[719,780,1050,1077]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="9 - 16" refId="ref63294" refString="Starkevich, P. &amp; Podenas, S. (2015) Taxonomic review of Tipula (Vestiplex) scripta Meigen, 1830 (Diptera: Tipulidae). Proceedings of the Academy of Natural Sciences of Philadelphia, 164, 9 - 16. https: // doi. org / 10.1635 / 053.164.0103" type="journal article" year="2015">2015</bibRefCitation>
). Males of 
<taxonomicName authority="Meigen, 1830" authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1830" box="[902,980,1051,1076]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scripta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[902,980,1051,1076]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">scripta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group are characterized by the following characters: gonocoxite horn-shaped, tergite 9 forming a pale yellow plate with posterior margin emarginated and anterior portion with transverse, elevated saucer. The members of the 
<taxonomicName authority="Meigen, 1830" authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1830" box="[897,975,1123,1148]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scripta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[897,975,1123,1148]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">scripta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group are distributed in the Holarctic and Oriental Regions. 
<taxonomicName authority="Alexander, 1916" authorityName="Alexander" authorityYear="1916" box="[358,810,1159,1185]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="caroliniana" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[358,430,1159,1185]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Tipula</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[447,468,1159,1184]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[485,615,1159,1185]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">caroliniana</emphasis>
Alexander, 1916
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Loew, 1863" authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1863" box="[822,1176,1159,1185]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longiventris" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[822,843,1159,1184]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[860,881,1159,1184]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[898,1032,1159,1185]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">longiventris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Loew, H." box="[1040,1176,1159,1185]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="275 - 326" refId="ref61595" refString="Loew, H. (1863) Diptera Americae septentrionalis indigena. Centuria quarta. Berliner Entomologische Zeitschrift, 7, 275 - 326. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 18630070104" type="journal article" year="1863">Loew, 1863</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Alexander, 1949" authorityName="Alexander" authorityYear="1949" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tacomicola" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[1236,1257,1159,1184]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1274,1295,1159,1184]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[1312,1436,1159,1185]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">tacomicola</emphasis>
Alexander, 1949
</taxonomicName>
are found in the Nearctic Region, 
<taxonomicName authority="Edwards, 1928" authorityName="Edwards" authorityYear="1928" box="[730,1098,1195,1221]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subscripta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[730,751,1195,1220]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[767,788,1195,1220]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[805,922,1195,1221]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">subscripta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Edwards, F. W." box="[929,1098,1195,1221]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="681 - 703" refId="ref60801" refString="Edwards, F. W. (1928) Some nematocerous Diptera from Yunnan and Tibet. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 10, 1, 681 - 703. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222932808672840" type="journal article" year="1928">Edwards, 1928</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is found in the East Palaearctic and Oriental Regions, and the remainder of species are found in the Palaearctic: 
<taxonomicName authority="Starkevich and Podenas, 2011" authorityName="Starkevich and Podenas" authorityYear="2011" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dhalma" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[1100,1122,1231,1256]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1138,1160,1231,1256]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[1176,1260,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">dhalma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Starkevich, P. &amp; Podenas, S." pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="141 - 147" refId="ref63233" refString="Starkevich, P. &amp; Podenas, S. (2011) A new species of long-palped crane fly in the subgenus Tipula (Vestiplex) [Diptera: Tipulidae] from the Far East of Russia. Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 137, 141 - 147. https: // doi. org / 10.3157 / 061.137.0103" type="journal article" year="2011">Starkevich and Podenas, 2011</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Riedel, 1913" authorityName="Riedel" authorityYear="1913" box="[326,665,1267,1293]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="intermixta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[326,347,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[362,384,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[398,513,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">intermixta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Riedel, M. P." box="[520,665,1267,1293]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 122" refId="ref62804" refString="Riedel, M. P. (1913) Die palaarktischen Arten der Dipteren-Gattung Tipula L. Abhandlungen des Vereins fur Naturwissenschaftliche Erforschung des Niederrheins (Bezirksgruppe des deutschen Lehrervereins fur Naturkunde). Krefeld, 1, 1 - 122." type="journal article" year="1913">Riedel, 1913</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Pierre, 1924" authorityName="Pierre" authorityYear="1924" box="[676,1026,1267,1293]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallidicosta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[676,697,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[712,733,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[748,880,1267,1293]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">pallidicosta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Pierre, C." box="[887,1026,1267,1293]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 159" refId="ref62426" refString="Pierre, C. (1924) Dipteres: Tipulidae. Faune de France, 8, 1 - 159." type="journal article" year="1924">Pierre, 1924</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Alexander, 1934" authorityName="Alexander" authorityYear="1934" box="[1036,1432,1267,1293]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallitergata" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[1036,1057,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1072,1094,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[1108,1239,1267,1293]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">pallitergata</emphasis>
Alexander, 1934
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Meigen, 1830" authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1830" box="[151,465,1303,1329]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scripta" subGenus="Vestiplex">
<emphasis box="[151,172,1303,1328]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">T.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[188,209,1303,1328]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">V.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[225,303,1303,1328]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">scripta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Meigen, J. W." box="[310,465,1303,1329]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="55 - 66" refId="ref62057" refString="Meigen, J. W. (1830) Systematische Beschreibung der bekannten europaischen zweiflugeligen Insekten. Sechster Theil. Gedrukt bei Beaufort Sohn, Bei Friedrich Wilhelm Forstmann, Aachen, xi + 401 pp., pls. 55 - 66." type="book chapter" year="1830">Meigen, 1830</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Savchenko, 1960" authorityName="Savchenko" authorityYear="1960" box="[520,919,1303,1329]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Tipula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semivittata" subGenus="Vestiplex">
