) 
<emphasis box="[593,716,1303,1328]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">semivittata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Savchenko, E. N." box="[723,919,1303,1329]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="143 - 216" refId="ref62891" refString="Savchenko, E. N. (1960) A contribution to the taxonomy of crane-flies (Diptera, Tipulidae) of the subgenus Vestiplex Bezzi of the genus Tipula L. Horae Societatis Entomologicae Rossicae Unionis Soveticae, 47, 143 - 216. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1960">Savchenko, 1960</bibRefCitation>
